Pretrained Model
The base pretrained model used before fine-tuning:
[Salesforce/blip-image-captioning-base]
Link: https://huggingface.co/Salesforce/blip-image-captioning-base
- Pretrained on 129 million image-caption pairs
- ViT vision encoder + BERT-style transformer decoder
- WordPiece tokenizer (~30k vocab)
